        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Too Narrow to Succeed Act </strong></p> <p>This bill requires federal institutional investors to report on their use of diverse-owned asset management firms. Additionally, the Department of Labor must conduct a survey of public- and private-sector pension plans regarding best practices for increasing the utilization and capacity of diverse-owned asset management firms.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
